# Secrets — Layer 1 of accidental-checkin defense.
# Layer 2 = gitleaks pre-commit hook (.pre-commit-config.yaml).
# Layer 3 = GitHub push protection (one-click in repo settings).
# Layer 4 = Anthropic dashboard spend cap.
# See README "Security guardrails" for the full setup.
*.secret.yaml
*.secret.yml
secret-*.yaml
secret-*.yml
api-keys.yaml
api-keys.yml
*.pem
*.key
# Don't ignore Helm chart templates that legitimately use these names
!charts/**/templates/**/*.yaml
!charts/**/templates/**/*.yml
